snippet.title: Phoning Home - Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Phoning Home is an open-world game of exploration and survival set on a strange, alien planet. It also tells the story of two robots -- ION and ANI – and their life-defining journey.
Available on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/431650
